p Runs the 'properties' test within the simulator (simulation times valid for 32bits architectures)

$ $SG_TEST_EXENV ./properties_simulator${EXEEXT:=} ${srcdir:=.}/../../platforms/prop.xml ${srcdir:=.}/properties.xml
